\begin{abstract} 
We give a new proof of the rectilinearization theorem of Hironaka. We deduce rectilinearization as a consequence of our theorem on local monomialization for complex and real analytic morphisms.
\end{abstract}





\maketitle

In this paper we  deduce Hironka's rectilinearization theorem  \cite{H}  as an application of our theorem on local monomialization for complex and real analytic morphisms \cite{C}.




